decision_conditions: The demolition of the "Block D"of Kellogg Tower, Park View Place, as detailed within the submitted documents, photographs and information, is considered to have been carried out in accordance with permissions Ref: 182843FUL and Ref: 224578CND. As such, the demolition was carried out lawfully and this certificate of lawfulness is hereby granted under Section 191 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990 (as amended).
description: Demolition of existing Block D (Lawful Development Certificate for an Existing Use/Development)
